data<-read.csv("Mydata.csv",row.names = 1,header = T)
data$LN<-log(data$Nlevel+1)
data$LIN<-log(data$IN)
data$Nadd <- factor(data$Nadd, levels = c("Ncess", "Ncont"))
relation<-lme(LIN ~ LN*Nadd,random = ~1|Block,data = data)
summary(relation)
